ce-strange-purple-flaregrid-artifact/</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"應該全線sony sensor行pdaf的都有呢個問題，差在同某 d 其他hardware 一齊運用時爆得大唔大鑊，即係 A7 一代果時，源用aps-c sensor的方法做粒低價 135ff cmos出來，攪到光暈 ufo極明顯一樣"},{"pid":"f520c72b3180e41b0fa30e13f5f69ccffcd498ac","tid":585102,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"885d8514004f7f8290d386d25212732f6283cbc8","tid":585102,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d21a85c88f422e0ef77c052387e92cfa797dc7c","tid":585102,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"X-Pro2出個陣有人研究過<br />\n<a href=\"https://petapixel.com/2017/02/23/fuji-cameras-produce-strange-purple-flaregrid-artifact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2Ffuji-cameras-produce-strange-purple-flaregrid-artifact%2F&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c40a62eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://petapixel.com/2017/02/23/fuji-cameras-produce-strange-purple-flaregrid-artifact/</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"應該全線sony sensor行pdaf的都有呢個問題，差在同某 d 其他hardware 一齊運用時爆得大唔大鑊，即係 A7 一代果時，源用aps-c sensor的方法做粒低價 135ff cmos出來，攪到光暈 ufo極明顯一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"減價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8194a4f5e353fa462fce7850ad85f8268a4d356c","tid":585102,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97a0a473ac214bffb827238fe142495f5be26922","tid":585102,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2a90445ba78af05bdeba65c7413c29c1053d8bf","tid":585102,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5c1eea3893433dca3ff1629880219eede38a68","tid":585102,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99b6ab503ef8d7280ffa51ea84fe1172d71db636","tid":585102,"uid":36157,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"連索尼打手都出手屌就知索尼Ｄ相機好唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f239644e93b5d39cb35995ba5af8484b5d45049b","tid":585102,"uid":107023,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"其實比起 A7一代 ufo 事件，今次我相信firmware 可解決，因為根本一向 on sensor 的pdaf 點，本身就係死點(某程度上也說明了點解 R3 只增大pdaf 範圍但不增加pdaf 點數目)<br />\n<br />\n當pdaf 對焦點越多，總像素不變的時候，源用番舊時的&quot;計算修補&quot;方法就可能令問題更明顯化，再加上所謂每一點 pdaf 未必只佔用了一個pixel...<br />\n當總像素只維持 24mp時，死點的佔有比高左，禁成像自然差左"},{"pid":"97873032d608576e3673d5ae6d18a54ada93f163","tid":585102,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ke9Q-LlPshA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fke9Q-LlPshA&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9b28639e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ke9Q-LlPshA</a><br />\nyoutube 都開始有測試同分析影片了，主要都係鬼佬果邊咬著唔放"},{"pid":"912c0a555c0e15804b094b1095fd62f57f60a14b","tid":585102,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97873032d608576e3673d5ae6d18a54ada93f163","tid":585102,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ke9Q-LlPshA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fke9Q-LlPshA&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9b28639e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ke9Q-LlPshA</a><br />\nyoutube 都開始有測試同分析影片了，主要都係鬼佬果邊咬著唔放"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"等睇索尼$0.50打手衝出香港去屌柒贏盡全球"},{"pid":"923e59702904617a7833d138cff22ff34600ac70","tid":585102,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"912c0a555c0e15804b094b1095fd62f57f60a14b","tid":585102,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97873032d608576e3673d5ae6d18a54ada93f163","tid":585102,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ke9Q-LlPshA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fke9Q-LlPshA&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9b28639e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ke9Q-LlPshA</a><br />\nyoutube 都開始有測試同分析影片了，主要都係鬼佬果邊咬著唔放"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"等睇索尼$0.50打手衝出香港去屌柒贏盡全球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"再有多個<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o-ao1FqRolc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo-ao1FqRolc&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=04749e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o-ao1FqRolc</a>"},{"pid":"aba7781ec50a73a1591c2fd9f4c4c32e8e37ff7b","tid":585102,"uid":51724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"所以nikon某高層話唔整on-sensor pdaf落自己d產品估計就係因為呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實用類似canon dual-pixel af的方式咪咩事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c77b105cc095f8990ace066cc1f691de6c8f4c1","tid":585102,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aba7781ec50a73a1591c2fd9f4c4c32e8e37ff7b","tid":585102,"uid":51724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"所以nikon某高層話唔整on-sensor pdaf落自己d產品估計就係因為呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實用類似canon dual-pixel af的方式咪咩事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T11:46:47.000Z","msg":"但係dual-pixel會降DR<br />\n6D2係例子"}]}